WEBVTT

24:17.030 --> 24:19.780 line:80%
I heard criminals were causing trouble
in Xigu Lane,

24:19.780 --> 24:21.800 line:80%
so I personally led men to take them down.

24:21.800 --> 24:23.590 line:80%
I didn't expect to meet you here, Lord Li.

24:23.590 --> 24:24.460 line:80%
Please forgive me

24:24.460 --> 24:26.120 line:80%
for not welcoming you sooner.
